game:decorbazaar-quickstart-text: Thank you for using my mod! This mod adds decorative items to the game. If anyone would love to help develop the mod, please contact me on discord @anyanana. Thank you to @EightTonnesOfCrab on discord for getting the stoves to function as well as the bath! Thank you to RikeiR for translating to Japanese! Enjoy! List of Items: New Ovens! These function as ovens, naturally. There are 7 types, 3 free-standing, 3 table top, and one meant to be put in the wall. To place the free standing ovens, you MUST place a temporary block where you would like to put the oven first. It can be a dirt block. Then you will place the free-standing oven on top of the temporary block, and then destroy the temporary block. Viola! An oven with fancy stuff underneath. Iron Oven is build to be placed in a wall. Stone Oven is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Oven with Glass is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Fancy Oven with Glass is a free-standing oven (see note above!). Table Stone Oven Table Oven with Glass Fancy Table Oven with Glass Stoves: These stoves currently function as ovens, though not visually. You can still see what is cooking by looking at the UI. Stone Stove Cast Iron Stove Cast Iron Stove with Firewood Cast Iron Stove V2 Cast Iron Fireplace Bathroom Decor: Bathroom Clutter Victorian Toilet Victorian Sink Claw Foot Tub allows for 100 buckets of water to fill up. Washing Tub Linen Basket Clothes Line Towel Rack Carpets: Carpets come in blue, dark black, gingham red, green, neutral, red, white, white dotted, yellow flower, dark fancy, and dark floral. Beds: All beds are functional :) Brass Bed Coffin Bed Flower Bed Purple Bed Tables: Side Tables right click to change type! Brass Table Coffee Table :right click to change variant. Cottage Core Table (Bald Cypress) Gothic Table Kitchen: All of the cabinet variants now have inner or corner types for those of you who want L shaped kitchens! Left Cabinet has storage slots. Right Cabinet has storage slots. Left Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Right Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Open Cabinet Stone Sinks Wood Sinks Double Wood & Stone sinks as well as the bald cypress sink now are able to contain water! To do this, you must place the water block, or empty a bucket, in the place you want to put the sink. The, you place the sink on top of where the water is flowing. If done correctly, it should stop overflowing and be completely contained within the sink. Infinite sink water! Stone Cabinet & Island has storage slots. Stone Drawer & Island has storage slots. Stone Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Stone Shelf has storage slots. Fancy Cabinet & Island has storage slots. Fancy Upper Cabinet has storage slots. Kitchen Clutter Ceramic Yellow Pot Jug Glass Tray Table Setting :right click to change variant. Deco Shelf Dish Rack Pots and Pans Mug Rack Bread Basket Wall Veggie Storage is functional. Veggie Storage is functional. Tea Sets Spice Rack has storage. Kitchen Shelf Bread Box has storage slots and can preserve food. Compost Bin should accelerate rot. Herb Rack Cooking Clutter : right click to change variant. Forraging Clutter : right click to change variant (more variants coming soon). Lamps: All Lamps are functional. Candelabras now have aged variant as well as most metal variants. Brass Lamps Right click to change type. Brass Sconce Goth Lamp Tall Candelabra Table Candelabra Seating: Cottage Core Stool (Bald Cypress) Fabric Chair Stool Sofas Victorian Lounge Chair Gothic Love Seat Fancy Gothic Chair Gothic Foot Rest Garden Decor: Garden Signs Bee Sign Potting Bench has storage slots for seeds. Seed Storage has storage slots for seeds. Terra Cotta Flower Pots are functional! Blue Flower Pot is functional! Purple Flower Pot is functional! Curtains: Curtains work where you right click to change whether you want the top (with the rod), middle, or bottom variant to be expressed for each block. There are currently a plain type and a fancy type. The color variants are: black, blue, brown, gray, green, orange, pink, plain, purple, red, white, and yellow. Random Stuff: Butter Churn Wooden Shelf : right click to change variant. Witchy Items Cartographer Map Sewing Shelf Twine Storage Wardrobe has slots for clothes. Brass Mirror Brass Candle Shelf Brass Mushroom Cloche Pile of Letters Sewing Shelf has storage. Twine Storage has storage. Graves : right click to change variant. Tile Blocks: Beige Tile Gray Tile Anthro Tile Aged Purple Tile Mossy Pink Tile Gold Square Tile Gold Meteor Tile Paintings available at Luxury, Furniture, and Artisan Traders! Fields of Grain House on the Hill Lone Grave White Flower Wallpapers available at Luxury, Furniture, and Artisan Traders!
